      <div class="use-case">
    <h3>Businesses</h3>
    <p>Zoom for client meetings and webinars. Meet for internal team calls. This use case demonstrates how the right tool can significantly improve productivity and outcomes. Users in this category should evaluate which platform better addresses their specific pain points and workflow requirements before making a decision.</p>
